{
  "texts": [
    "It should be noted that although JSON-style outcomes are generated by LLMs after analyzing the text-based well records, the current workflow does not have the capability to save the outputs directly as local JSON files.",
    "Therefore, an additional post-processing step is required to save the information extraction outputs as local files.",
    "Let's now examine the final extraction performance for the four prompts across the 160 well records in Colorado and Pennsylvania.",
    "Given the fact that the well records from the U.S. are not in the same format, we here evaluate the performance of LLMs for information extraction separately.",
    "Again as introduced in Section 2, we used AOS as the metric for performance evaluation."
  ]
}